name: qiaoxitech
short_description:
Qiaoxi Tech Co.,Ltd founded in the year of 2008, is a high-tech company engaged in scientific researching, manufacturing, Marketing, technical support and service of high power LED bulbs,LED Light, led spotlight ,led lighting. With modern corporation management system and QC system, our company is an all-around corporation which gathers design, exploitation, production and distribution. 

Our main products range: 

LED Street light, 
LED wall washer, 
LED panel light, 
LED ceiling/down light, 
LED floodlight/tunnel light, 
LED underwater light, 
LED underground/inground light, 
LED tube light , 
LED high bay light/industrial light. 
LED strip/rigid bar light,etc 
If any special requests, we may produce and design for you. 
OEM is acceptable. 
With its high quality and reasonable prices, our products are well received in many countries and regions, including Europe, North &South America, Middle East and So on.
